quran[7{c,v,t}:
2,70,"phir bolay apne Rab se saaf saaf pooch kar batao kaisi gaaye matloob hai, hamein is ki taayun mein ishtibaah ho gaya hai Allah ne chaha, to hum is ka pata paleen ge"
2,71,"( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ne jawab diya : Allah kehta hai ke woh aisi gaaye hai jis se khidmat nahi li jati, nah zameenjotti hai nah pani khainchti hai, sahih salim aur bay daagh hai, is par woh pukaar utthay ke haan, ab tum ne theek pata bataya hai phir unhon ne usay zibah kya, warna woh aisa karte maloom nah hotay thay"
2,72,"aur tumhe yaad hai woh waqea jab tum ne aik shakhs ki jaan li thi, phir is ke baray mein jhagrnay aur aik dosray par qatal ka ilzaam thopne lagey thay aur Allah ne faisla kar liya tha ke jo kuch tum chupatay ho, usay khol kar rakh day ga"
2,73,uss waqt hum ne hukum diya ke maqtool ki laash ko is ke aik hissay se zarb lagao dekho is terhan Allah mُurdon ko zindagi bkhshta hai aur tumhe apni nishanain dekhata hai taakay tum samjhoo
2,74,"magar aisi nishanain dekhnay ke baad bhi aakhir-kaar tumahray dil sakht hogaye, patharon ki taraf sakht, balkay sakhti mein kuch un se bhi barhay hue, kyunkay patharon mein se to koi aisa bhi hota hai jis mein se chashmay phoot bahtay hain, koi phutta hai aur is mein se pani nikal aata hai aur koi Khuda ke khauf se laraz kar gir bhi parta hai Allah tumahray kartoton se bay khabar nahi hai"
2,75,ae muslmano! ab kya inn logon se tum yeh tawaqqa rakhtay ho ke tumhari dawat par imaan le ayen ge? halaank un mein se aik giroh ka Shewa yeh raha hai ke Allah ka kalaam suna aur phir khoob samajh boojh kar danista is mein tahreef ki
2,76,"( Mohammad rasoolSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam par ) imaan laane walon se mlitay hain to kehte hain ke hum bhi inhen mantay hain, aur jab aapas mein aik dosray se takhliye ki baat cheet hoti hai to kehte hain ke bay waqoof hogaye ho? inn logon ko woh baatein batatay ho jo Allah ne tum par kholi hain taakay tumahray Rab ke paas tumahray muqablay mein inhen hujjat? mein paish karen"
